  "text": "Microdissected tumor and normal DNA samples from eight hyalinizing trabecular tumors (discovery set) were subjected to whole-exome sequencing (WES, n = 3) [CITATION_1] and to Memorial Sloan Kettering-Integrated Mutation Profiling of Actionable Cancer Targets (MSK-IMPACT) sequencing (n = 5; Fig. 1 ), which targets all exons and selected introns of 410 cancer genes, as previously described [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] (Supplementary Table S1 ). Three additional cases from the validation set were also subjected to MSK-IMPACT ( Fig. 1 ).",
